Welcome to SunshineBSD — an opinionated desktop BSD.

 * Configuration lives in /etc/sunshine/*.lua  (run: sunconfig check)
 * Services are supervised by runit            (run: sv status <name>)
 * The system snapshots itself before changes  (rollback is one boot away)
